replyContent:
Hi Renlid1,
Yes, the storyline is the same for all versions. The versions differ by the mode of payment and by the availability of the extra features. If you purchase the full version or the full unlock of the free trial version, the game is added to your library, which is convenient if you plan to replay it later.
Best regards,
FIVE-BN Games

content: SO VERY DISAPPOINTED!!! Froze up constantly AND even CRASHED! Took 3 days to finish JUST because I got tired of restarting the game! Has hidden objects and morphing objects throughout. SO dark making it so difficult to see them so I looked for the collectibles BUT didn't even bother with the morphing! With ALL the problems and glitches it's DEFINITELY NOT worth the exorbitant PRICE!!! I won't be playing this GAME AGAIN like I usually do!!!
replyContent:
Hi Koki,
We are sorry to see that you're unsatisfied with this game. 
We don't know what caused the issues you described as the game worked fine during the testing. Please report this issue to our tech support (support@five-bn.com) so that our specialists could check your game files and find the reason for your difficulties.
Regards,
FIVE-BN Team
